I understand the nameds have a quest piece that goes with Dozekar, but that was not listed on the rotation.  Now for you to come on and say that the nameds are now part of the rotation is basically making up rules as you go and stepping on everyone else who can or have been killing the MOBS in question.  Its like saying dont kill the golems in Fear anymore cause they are now on the Cazic Rotation.  Well that just screwed the people who have been able to kill the golems and not CT. <br>
